<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="PT-br">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image" sizes="96x96" href="/images/favicon.png">
  <title>LocadoRafa</title>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-dark ml-auto ml-md-0">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><img class="img-responsive" src="/images/logo.png" width="50" height="ml-auto" alt="" /></a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <%- include('./partials/sidebar')%>

  <main class="page-content">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <h2>Bem vindo!<%= user.nome %></h2>
      <hr>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="form-group col-md-12">
          <p>Utilize o menu ao lado para navegar.</p>
          <br>
          <p>Escolha seu filme e clique em <span class="badge badge-warning"> Alugar</span>. Caso deseje devolver o
            filme, clique em <span class="badge badge-info"> Devolver</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <img src="/images/filme_fundo.png" class="img-fluid" alt="imagem alegre de filmes">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>




  <%- include('./partials/footer')%>

  <script src="/javascripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/scriptUser.js"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/b5ed3fff72.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>